{"tid":1658830,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"10月20號 尖沙咀 打 何 妖","createTime":"2019-10-16T15:40:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T13:07:24.000Z","uid":326930,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f3bce541df4c585975bba098e518393912dea249","tid":1658830,"uid":326930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:40:53.000Z","msg":"子杰哥件事，目前人已經穩定，不幸中之大幸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家要集中既事，只有一件：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kwoPAUS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkwoPAUS.jpg&h=e1b0c81f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他都係其次！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">有個香港人藍絲廢佬打人，唔通你搞晒全香港人？？？<br />\n<br />\n手足，唔應該以一個種族為目標<br />\n應以針對形式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要搵果幾個南亞人出來唔難架，你俾10萬出去，5分鐘搞掂。<br />\n要搞既，應針對果幾件傻hi，而唔係一個民族<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幫幫手，我地而家已經焦頭爛額，要應對政府既分化、黑警既濫權、藍紅絲廢佬既暴力、的士佬亂撞人、手足既冤案、國際戰線、中資黑幫裝修等等。。。<br />\n<br />\n唔好在新增，我地唔係做呢啲次緊急既野，對準政權，光復香港才是重中之重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有事？打何妖<br />\n無事？打何妖<br />\n唔知乜事？打何妖<br />\n心情唔好？打何妖<br />\n想去買鞋？打何妖<br />\n唔知做乜？打何妖<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n10.20 Sun 1:30pm 尖沙咀遊行，出來打何妖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他行動/建議，請暫時不要再討論，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記住遊行、裝修中資福建鄉黑、打何妖</span></span>"},{"pid":"f79e9ee7aca78048313f09ccc4b10ff9610c2e6b","tid":1658830,"uid":47852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T10:45:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd5eff7aaf88efaaa2ab0103a813ac64117520f1","tid":1658830,"uid":296410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T13:07:24.000Z","msg":"不了，唔想同何妖宣傳"}]}